channel.title: TC/IP Help
channel.description:
Hey, im new to servers and everything, ive read around, I know people are tired of noobs, like me asking for server help, but heres MY problem
I created a server using the server builder stickied.
The only reason i did this was because when i try to log in to my router, i enter my router ip into IE and it does not go to the router page liek ive seen. I have a wireless internet connection, and SBC DSL, when i enter the given linksys address (not the one shown in my internet connection) it comes up with the sbc page, where there are modem options. But none however, have a field for creating a new TC/IP
help?
please...[br][size=1]Posted on: April 16, 2007, 07:57:35 PM[/size][hr]bump
